1.docker service is noting but running same container service cross mutiple containers
2.this is a kind of loadbalancing 

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
example

docker service create --name {name of the service}  image

in the official docker documentaion it looks like this

docker service create --name {name of the service} image 'ping docker.com' this is called arguements

these arguements are not required when we pass a CMD or ENTRYPOINT.sh in our dockerfile
